{"tid":548575,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"用 AMD THREADRIPPER CPU 掘礦有利可圖？九個月即回本","createTime":"2018-02-02T16:32:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T02:40:57.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d2bbe769093f0936a11ebb6ed60fc00e2c12ff28","tid":548575,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T16:32:55.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">講起掘礦，大家都會聯想到是用大量顯示卡來掘吧？所以顯示卡才被礦工搶購一空，價格飆升。不過原來 CPU 都可以用來掘礦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？還要是有利可圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？這並不是指 Pirate Bay 透過網站來使用瀏覽者電腦 CPU 資源來掘礦那種，而是指用 AMD Ryzen Threadripper 系列 CPU 組裝私人掘礦機，回本期還不需一年呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/23588-ryzen-threadripper-pib-front-facing-1260x709-768x432.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F23588-ryzen-threadripper-pib-front-facing-1260x709-768x432.png&h=689d3118&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/2018/02/02/%E7%94%A8amd-threadripper-cpu%E6%8E%98%E7%A4%A6%E6%9C%89%E5%88%A9%E5%8F%AF%E5%9C%96-%E4%B9%9D%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E5%8D%B3%E5%9B%9E%E6%9C%AC/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2F2018%2F02%2F02%2F%25E7%2594%25A8amd-threadripper-cpu%25E6%258E%2598%25E7%25A4%25A6%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%259C%2596-%25E4%25B9%259D%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%258D%25B3%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%259C%25AC%2F&d=09cucnzjOCWgK%2B46BQjIg5UJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=7500f5a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/2018/02/02/%E7%94%A8amd-threadripper-cpu%E6%8E%98%E7%A4%A6%E6%9C%89%E5%88%A9%E5%8F%AF%E5%9C%96-%E4%B9%9D%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E5%8D%B3%E5%9B%9E%E6%9C%AC/</a></div>"},{"pid":"b6a328404596b90a461bc5c0b8732982daba2f73","tid":548575,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T16:34:41.000Z","msg":"據外媒 PCGamesN 報道， AMD 技術行銷經理 Damien Triolet 告訴他們：「其實 AMD Threadripper CPU 是很適合用來組台家用掘礦機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，而且其掘礦潛力亦相當可觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。」不是 GPU 才對於掘礦這種平行運算更有優勢嗎？用 CPU 掘礦應該會掘得很慢吧？其實只要選擇適合 CPU 掘礦機的虛擬貨幣和演算法，即使是用 CPU 來掘礦，亦有利可圖。例如 CryptoNight 這個演算法，本身就是針對一般家用電腦的 CPU 而設，每條 Mining Thread 需要多達 2MB 的 L3 Cache 快取記憶體，而顯示卡所使用的 GDDR5 記憶體不及 CPU 的 L3 Cache 快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ， ASIC 掘礦機亦通常都不具備那麼大容量的記憶體，所以 CPU 就正好用來掘 CryptoNight 的貨幣，例如是 Monero 門羅幣之類。<br />\n<br />\n因此， Damien Triolet 認為 AMD Threadripper CPU 很適合用來掘這類貨幣。 AMD Ryzen Threadripper 1950X 具備 16 核 32 線程（ Thread ）， L3 Cache 多達 32MB ，撇除系統可能會佔 1 &ndash; 2 條 Thread，就最多可以分配 15 條 Thread 來進行 CryptoNight 掘礦（15 Threads x 2MB Cache = 30MB Cache &lt; 32MB ）。而 Ryzen Threadripper 1920X 亦具備 12C24T 和 32MB L3 Cache，所以整體來説， AMD Threadripper 系列比 Intel 的 CPU 有更高的掘礦能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （如 Intel i9-7900X 就只有 13.75MB L3 Cache）。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/intel-spec-768x286.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2Fintel-spec-768x286.png&h=851d4b25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">同樣是 Intel HEDT 平台，Intel 的 CPU 就不及 AMD Threadripper 有那麼多 L3 Cache。</span></div>"},{"pid":"ee14a14e75bb05dbc969f2974ad02c75e8cc8803","tid":548575,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T16:35:43.000Z","msg":"Damien Triolet 亦表示 AMD Threadripper CPU 在 NiceHash 平台，可以 CryptoNight 演算法每個月賺 $90 美元（約 $702 港元，已扣除電力費用，以美國當時的情況計算）。雖然用 Threadripper 高昂的價格，來買顯示卡掘其他虛擬貨幣（如 SHA-256 演算法的 Bitcoin）可能比較合符成本效益，但他認為購買了 Threadripper 的砌機玩家，可在不使用電腦時，考慮把電腦用來掘礦，以 Threadripper 1920X 在當地的最低售價 $760 美元（約 $5,928）來説，只需 9 個月就能回本，可謂掘礦能幫助補貼電腦的成本。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/amd-hk-price-threadripper.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2Famd-hk-price-threadripper.png&h=0c829650&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">香港的電費與 Threadripper CPU 的成本與美國不同，所以回本期亦有所差異。</span></div>"},{"pid":"41c17cde513f34d9a3445aacdfbec33ba627d384","tid":548575,"uid":82970,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T17:01:59.000Z","msg":"冇人性，連CPU都唔放過<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"907af74548baf4cdacf176de798e93def124e180","tid":548575,"uid":49852,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T18:20:55.000Z","msg":"已經入手左一打到時10k一粒放出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b698eba2ed0d8a2f270167435459073c3e41279","tid":548575,"uid":9115,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T18:24:36.000Z","msg":"9個月後虛擬貨幣仲值唔值錢都成問題"},{"pid":"85d60e6ba4df890cd7302cef9f8eb5d0e0083b29","tid":548575,"uid":2507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T18:24:51.000Z","msg":"以後係唔係所有CPU GPU畀挖礦撚玩曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8088f55747bbbf7f19fdf5cdf0d9deffd2467a3a","tid":548575,"uid":60695,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T04:21:40.000Z","msg":"Advance Mining Devices<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8cca293102cd5eda91903911006d847f85ec7ca","tid":548575,"uid":28563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T04:38:10.000Z","msg":"仲nicehash<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce46a48f754b601221c243a8ae0f6f58c8f8a054","